channel.title: Me, Pure2, and Kihomura
channel.description:
Okay, so i was on The forums just like, 10 mins ago, and i saw Davids cooking party. So i said "Ill go, why not" so i went into the cc and there was Pure2ownage and Kihomura. They told me to come to lumbi world 16, so i go there and i see kiho approaching men saying funny ass lines like, "Im soooooo erectic" and stuff. Me and pure were trying to find him a girl to make him straight (this is a joke) and he kept hitting on men. Now me, kiho and some other guy are running around varrock trying to find a man that will merry kiho, that is if runescape doesnt have a law against gay marrage :|
Ill post screenies soon, this is tooo funny.
